      * <TOTEM:PARA. guseravv-Ev-Before-Program>
           move LK-BL-PROG-ID    TO COMO-PROG-ID.
           copy resource ".\elemento.bmp".
           call "W$BITMAP" using wbitmap-load, "elemento.bmp"
                          giving elemento-bmp 
           .
